cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as it focuses on rendering 2D images from 3D shapes. It also involves computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with image processing and inverse rendering tasks. The use of deep learning techniques suggests that it may also fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper's focus on differentiable rendering suggests that it may also be relevant to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
